20-12-23\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                            \u003Cchange when=\"2021-02-22\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa encoded text division, cleaned up the autogenerated text and checked the edition\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic002953_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic002953.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Corig>ΕΟ\u003C/orig>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Corig>Α\u003C/orig>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Corig>ΛΕ\u003C/orig>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003Corig>ΥΕΟ\u003C/orig>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Corig>Ε\u003C/orig>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text after Maniscalco 2015\u003C/note> \u003C!-- or Fiorentini, check both -->\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--a reused fragment of an architrave (employed in the C4 phase of a chthonic sanctuary, just to the east of Cittadella in Contrada San Francesco). Antonaccio states that other than Fiorentini's note and photo it remains unpublished. I don't think it has been picked up by SEG (it's not in 1980 - 1986); Fiorentini's phrasing is ambiguous, and the inscription doesn't look archaic to me; I think Fiorentini means that this piece should be attributed to the C4 phase, and was found in re-use. Fiorentini doesn't publish the inscription itself other than a good b/w photograph. Maniscalco (2015) suggests that this may be part of base of a sundial; and says it's not locatable in Aidone or Morgantina-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Fiorentini\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1980-1981\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>598 tav.85\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/A6SAMXVZ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001989\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001989\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Maniscalco\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2015\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange/> \u003C!-- check -->\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/NM78J5GN\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002536\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002536\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n\t       \u003Cbibl>\n\t           \u003Cauthor>Antonaccio\u003C/author>\n\t           \u003Cdate>1999\u003C/date>\n\t           \u003CcitedRange>88 n.3\u003C/citedRange>\n\t           \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/HIA724KT\"/>\n\t       \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002180\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002180\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n\t   \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
